{
  "texts": [
    "Using the patent number, we merge the Reliance on Science and USPTO patent datasets.",
    "After merging, we find that one or more renewed patents cite 4.93% of papers in our training sample.",
    "For this analysis, we assume that firms do not commercially apply papers not cited by a renewed patent.",
    "We train the commercial potential models by developing one model per year from 2000 to 2020, resulting in 21 models.",
    "Each model is trained independently using the same procedure with timeconstrained data."
  ]
}